flowchart TB
    Start(["ğŸ‘¥  User accesses **myapp.com/***"]) --> InitState@{ label: "<span style=\"font-family:\">ğŸ“&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>**Initial State**<br>st.session_state = { }<br>authenticated = False<br>cookies = [ ]" }
    InitState --> GetCookies["ğŸª&nbsp; **Check cookies**<br>(look for *auth token* in cookies or context headers)"]
    GetCookies --> TokenCheck@{ label: "â”&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:\">ğŸ‘¤  </span>**Check active user session**. Is there any *auth token* in session?" }
    TokenCheck == No ==> NoToken["**âŒ&nbsp; &nbsp;No Token Found**"]
    TokenCheck == Yes ==> TokenExistsInSession["âœ…&nbsp; Token exists in session"]
    NoToken --> SSORedirect["ğŸšªğŸ”&nbsp; Redirection to **SSO login URL**<br>*login.microsoftonline.com/**"]
    SSORedirect --> Credentials@{ label: "<span style=\"color:\">ğŸ”“ </span>**Are credentials valid?** <br>(vs IdP)" }
    Credentials == Yes ==> ValidCreds["ğŸ†•&nbsp; Backend returns generated JWT token from SAML response"]
    Credentials == No ==> InvalidCreds["âŒ&nbsp; Invalid login"]
    InvalidCreds -- Retry login --> SSORedirect
    ValidCreds ==> TokenExistsInSession
    TokenExistsInSession --> ValidateToken{"ğŸ”‘&nbsp; **JWT token decoding...**<br> Is it valid?"}
    ValidateToken == "No<br>(error, expired...)" ==> Rerun@{ label: "<span style=\"color:\">ğŸ”&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>**st.rerun**" }
    ValidateToken == Yes ==> TokenValid["**Extract Claims**<br>(e.g., username, email, etc.)"]
    Rerun -- "**authenticated = False** <br>cookies/headers cleared (if existed)" --> NoToken
    TokenValid --> AuthState["ğŸ‘¤&nbsp; **Authenticated state**<br>authenticated = True<br>{username: ..., email: ...}"]
    AuthState ==> ActiveSession["ğŸŸ¢&nbsp; &nbsp;**Active Session**"]
    ActiveSession -- ğŸŒ&nbsp; HTTP request to backend --> TokenRefresh@{ label: "<span style=\"color:\">ğŸ”  </span>**Sliding Session**:<br>Extend token expiration (+*ACCESS_TOKEN_REFRESH_MINUTES*)" }
    ActiveSession -- âŒ›&nbsp; User Inactivity (&gt;*ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRATION_MINUTES* without requests) --> TokenExpired["âŒ› **Token Expired**"]
    ActiveSession -- ğŸ”„&nbsp; &nbsp;User refreshes browser --> BrowserRefresh["ğŸ†•&nbsp; **Clears old session state + opens new session**"]
    TokenRefresh --> ActiveSession
    TokenExpired -- ğŸš«&nbsp; Error 401: Unauthorized --> SSORedirect
    BrowserRefresh -- **authenticated = False**<br>cookies/headers remain (if existed)--> InitState
    InitState@{ shape: rect}
    TokenCheck@{ shape: diamond}
    Credentials@{ shape: diamond}
    Rerun@{ shape: rect}
